snippet.title: Grand Theft Auto: Vice City – The Definitive Edition Comparison Video
snippet.description:
Grand Theft Auto: Vice City takes players back to the 1980s and into a neon-soaked tropical town brimming with excess through the story of Tommy Vercetti and his quest for revenge. 

Available now as part of Grand Theft Auto: The Trilogy – The Definitive Edition: http://rsg.ms/42b361b
